B.Z9=new A.bL(B.ej,["What are Goins?","Goins are MiniGuru's virtual currency. Your child earns Goins by uploading project videos, getting likes and comments. Goins can be spent in the MiniGuru shop on STEAM materials."],t.d)
B.Z5=new A.bL(B.ej,["How does a parent top up the wallet?","Go to your child's Profile \u2192 Wallet \u2192 Add Money. You can add any amount via Razorpay (UPI, card, or net banking). The balance is then available for your child to spend in the shop."],t.d)
B.Za=new A.bL(B.ej,["How does ordering from the shop work?","Your child browses the shop, adds items to cart, and checks out using their wallet balance. You receive a confirmation and the materials are physically dispatched to your delivery address."],t.d)
B.Z6=new A.bL(B.ej,["Is my child's data safe?","Yes. MiniGuru is DPDPA 2023 compliant. We never sell data, never show ads, and all content is moderated before publication. See our Privacy Policy for full details."],t.d)
B.Z8=new A.bL(B.ej,["How is content moderated?","Every project video is reviewed by a trained MiniGuru moderator before it goes live. No personal details of the child may appear in published content."],t.d)
B.Z4=new A.bL(B.ej,["Can I delete my child's account?","Yes. Email privacy@miniguru.in with your registered phone number and we will delete all data within 30 days, as required by DPDPA 2023."],t.d)
